                <h3 class="subheading">Connected Car Technology: Smarter Than Ever</h3>
                <p>The new Renault Duster comes with an impressive suite of connected services, offering convenience, security, and peace of mind. </p>
                <h5 class="subheading">Connected Features Include:</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Stolen vehicle tracking </span>to help recover the vehicle</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Remote lock and unlock </span>functionality</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Remote pre-conditioning </span>to set cabin temperature before entering</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Find your Renault, </span>allowing users to locate their vehicle easily</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Remote tyre pressure monitoring</span></li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Firmware Over-The-Air (FOTA) updates,</span> ensuring the system stays up to date</li>
                </ul>
                <p>These features reflect Renault’s commitment to integrating smart technology into everyday driving. </p>

